uwcattext:
Thanks to the University of Wyoming Catering & Events, we are able to provide you a meal today. You will get to choose a meal from their menu, and the meal will be given to you during this study.

Please take a moment to read the below text describing the services offered by UW Catering & Events.
Catering & Events has a comprehensive menu that includes buffets, plated meals, hors 
d’oeuvres, bakery items, desserts and beverages. It offers a diverse and savory range of cuisine that will satisfy the palate of virtually any audience, with a calorie content ranging between 400 and 1000 calories per meal.
Its experienced staff is capable of 
providing these menu offerings through full-service (waited, 
buffet-style, reception) or limited service (delivery, pick-up). No 
matter the occasion, Catering & Events’ delicious options and 
precise organization are sure to make any event a crowd pleaser.
